{"tid":1582622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"cls 有樂團錄咗個mv送比一眾抗爭者！","createTime":"2019-09-20T07:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T04:50:31.000Z","uid":28870,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"64d9714387c91bac9dd19ce4f345b9809e919b5f","tid":1582622,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"Source from: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/frontlinelive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffrontlinelive&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8rccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=9a7de036\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/frontlinelive</a><br />\n<br />\n百人灌錄屬於這個時代的《Do you hear the People Sing》 <br />\n<br />\n音樂人一呼百應，在短時間內組成了40位的管弦樂團和60多位的合唱團去錄製三個語言（廣東話、英語、國語）的《Do you hear the people sing》；亦聚集了社會上各界人士進行MV 拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n廣東話：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o8KX0PboIvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do8KX0PboIvU&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8rccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=cf42c636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o8KX0PboIvU</a><br />\n<br />\n英語：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IweBON1Bv_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIweBON1Bv_U&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8rccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=ef471752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IweBON1Bv_U</a><br />\n國語：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6Geu2bybr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do6Geu2bybr0&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8rccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=25112e95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6Geu2bybr0</a>"},{"pid":"be3bf031077f5d4a3d0e500af6e8b2d9752e34a5","tid":1582622,"uid":28870,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"選擇這首歌，目的是提醒香港人不要失去希望，鼓勵大家挺身而出，齊心吶喊，進一步為民主抗爭；亦想以這首歌向每一個香港人致敬，亦向世界作出呼喚：為良知站出來，向高牆齊聲吶喊。<br />\n<br />\n錄音過程中，有很多難忘的畫面：當中有樂手放棄自己手上的工作，配合短短的錄音檔期；因為交通擠塞，有樂手怕趕不及時間到達場地，徒步背著重重的樂器趕達現場......為的是想盡其所能，為這場運動做點事。<br />\n<br />\n的確，未必每人都可以上到前線，但大家很想盡自己能力為這場運動付出。我們不知道這場抗爭要撐多久，所以我們要更加齊心，更不要失去希望。MV 的拍攝概念就是如此，各人期望抗爭到最後，可以在煲底相見。<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝各位手足的付出，不論是指揮、樂手、歌者、錄音師、混音師、資助場錄音及拍攝場地的有心人、各行各業的演員、拍攝團隊和器材的支援...... 促成這次製作！香港人真真正正we connect!<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n香港人 加油"},{"pid":"b4c34f5eaa6c3b2e0cb9e99cb7e8c1f61810e3d4","tid":1582622,"uid":27918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"[<strong><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">加拿大撚入</span></strong></strong>] <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>第一次</ins></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>海外</ins></span><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>大型</ins></span><span style=\"color: red;\">籌款</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(好似係)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1582473/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1582473/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"845f0539a07908f7fd307062cedcfb24bee4f77e","tid":1582622,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26cfd64d8d87bc987022fb3dac1c2de1e0920116","tid":1582622,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53113bc9cebe7fff3fe7886c78253be2382cf750","tid":1582622,"uid":208429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"知恩巴"},{"pid":"8d682e0c713fd553ad35cbc639b22fce47a75a6c","tid":1582622,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br /